color: #8b9dc3" target=3D"_blank">this is now a matter of public record</a>=
. =E2=80=9CYes or no, does Facebook use audio obtained from mobile devices =
to enrich personal information about users?=E2=80=9D he asked. =E2=80=9CNo,=
